{"tid":1783724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反彈劾嘅民主黨議員 Rep. Jeff Van Drew 宣布將會轉入共和黨","createTime":"2019-12-15T05:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T06:59:36.000Z","uid":236171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e30198170ea10e6f47342d8703f8aaf2b869d2","tid":1783724,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都係嗰句，美國黨派之爭我哋盡量唔好干預。呢度純粹分享下新聞咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Rep. Jeff Van Drew expected to switch parties after Trump meeting</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nOfficials said Saturday that Rep. Jeff Van Drew of New Jersey, a vocally anti-impeachment Democrat, will join the Republican Party in the coming days.<br />\n<br />\nThe decision, they said, came after Van Drew joined President Trump for a lengthy Friday meeting, during which Trump urged him to join the GOP.<br />\n<br />\nVan Drew  has been a critical voice opposing impeachment inside the Democratic ranks, saying the process is too divisive and comes too close to the 2020 presidential election to be worth pursuing. Van Drew has positioned himself at the rightmost flank of his party, though he has generally voted in line with the leadership on major bills."},{"pid":"e15028f2ca58f3e1a03c5dc6e6b933b94ab34298","tid":1783724,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"Source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/powerpost/trump-urges-rep-van-drew-anti-impeachment-democrat-to-switch-parties/2019/12/14/b201bb4a-1ea0-11ea-8d58-5ac3600967a1_story.html#click=https://t.co/BSxwYXsZpm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpowerpost%2Ftrump-urges-rep-van-drew-anti-impeachment-democrat-to-switch-parties%2F2019%2F12%2F14%2Fb201bb4a-1ea0-11ea-8d58-5ac3600967a1_story.html%23click%3